WEBVTT

00:03:29.666 --> 00:03:32.346
kama ile hali iliyoitangulia Big Bang.

00:03:32.346 --> 00:03:35.276
Hii ndiyo Uchakacho Mkubwa.

00:03:35.276 --> 00:03:39.576
Je hii sehemu ndogo ya mata inaweza
kulipuka kuwa Mlipuko Mkubwa mwingine?

00:03:39.576 --> 00:03:43.419
Ulimwengu unaweza kuongezeka na
kujifunga tena na tena,

00:03:43.419 --> 00:03:45.729
ikirudia historia yake yote?

00:03:45.729 --> 00:03:50.119
Nadharia inayoeleza ulimwengu huo
unajulikana kama Mruko Mkubwa.

00:03:50.119 --> 00:03:54.829
Pia hamna namna ya kujua miruko
mingapi imeshatokea tayari---

00:03:54.829 --> 00:03:57.447
au mingapi itatokea huko mbeleni.

00:03:57.447 --> 00:04:03.037
Kila mruko itafuta mbali kumbukumbu yeyote
ya historia ya ulimwengu ya nyuma.